metadata.title: NA session begins as budget debate enters sixth day

content.article_body: ISLAMABAD, Jun 19 (APP):The National Assembly session, chaired by Speaker Ayaz Sadiq, commenced at 11:06 AM on Thursday. Lawmakers are set to continue deliberations on the Finance Bill 2025-26 for the sixth day, with active participation expected as members scrutinize various aspects of the proposed federal budget.
